# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000629> (emission of radiation)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000629> "emission of radiation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000629> "The emission radiation is a process describing the release of energy in the form of electromagnetic waves or particles from a material."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000629> obo:BFO_0000015)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000635> (evolution of damage)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000635> "evolution of damage"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000635> "An evolution of damage is a process representing the progression of material degradation under mechanical, thermal, or chemical stresses."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000635> obo:BFO_0000015)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000661> (glass)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000661> "It is often composed of silica-based compounds."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000661> "glass"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000661> "A glass is an engineered material present as an amorphous solid typically formed by rapid cooling of a melt."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000661> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000002>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000663> (kristallit)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000663> "crystallite"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000663> "kristallit"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000663> "Korn"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000663> "grain"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000663> "A crystal grain is a crystal that is part of a polycrystal."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000663> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020003>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000773> (hardness)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000773> "hardness"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000773> "The hardness is a mechanical property used as a measure of a material's resistance to localized plastic deformation, often tested by indentation or scratch methods."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000773> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000848>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000777> (heat capacity)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000777> "heat capacity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000777> "The heat capacity is a thermal property describing the amount of heat energy required to raise the temperature of a material by a given amount."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000777> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000981>)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000777> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001029> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000549>))

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000794> (injection molding machine)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000794> "Spritzgießmaschine"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000794> "injection molding machine"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000794> "An Injection Molding Machine is a Device used to produce plastic parts by injecting molten plastic into molds under high pressure."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000794> "Eine Spritzgießmaschine ist ein Gerät, das verwendet wird, um Kunststoffteile durch Einspritzen von geschmolzenem Kunststoff in Formen unter hohem Druck herzustellen."@de)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000794> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000602>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000802> (irradiation process)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000802> "irradiation process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000802> "An irradiation process is a process in which a radiation source (bearing a stimulus role) emits radiation towards a material entity (bearing the target role)"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000802> obo:BFO_0000015)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> (manufacturing process)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> "Manufacturing processes alternate qualities of materials, i.e., a value specification of some quality of a material entity, which is a specified input to the process, cannot be the same as a value specification of the same quality of another material entity, which is a specified output of the process. 

Unfortunately is is not possible to write down such axiom based on OWL. Semi-working solution are the temporally qualified continuants + SPARQL constrains."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> "Herstellungsprozess"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> "manufacturing process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> "A planned process that is driven by the primary intent to transform objects
A manufacturing process is always a transformative process."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> "Ein geplannter Prozess, der von der primären Absicht angetrieben wird, Objekte zu transformieren. Ein Herstellungsprozess ist immer ein Transformationsprozess."@de)
EquivalentClasses(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> ObjectIntersectionOf(obo:OBI_0000011 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(obo:OBI_0000293 ObjectUnionOf(obo:BFO_0000027 obo:BFO_0000030)) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(obo:OBI_0000299 ObjectUnionOf(obo:BFO_0000027 obo:BFO_0000030))))
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> obo:OBI_0000011)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(obo:OBI_0000293 ObjectUnionOf(obo:BFO_0000027 obo:BFO_0000030)))
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(obo:OBI_0000299 ObjectUnionOf(obo:BFO_0000027 obo:BFO_0000030)))

