AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000845> "matrix role"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000845> "Matrix is the role of a PortionOfConnectedMatter that implies to host the Filler."@en)
