AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000848> "A mechanical property is a material property that inheres in a material M when an object O_target that consists of M is stimulated in a process through an interaction with an object O_stimulus and M changes its stress/strain/..(mechanical?) SDCs.

TODO: Check general class axiom and defintion altogether !!!"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000848> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000005>)
