AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000853> "The crystallographic texture is a morphological quality describing the arrangement and orientation of grains in a metallic material, observed through crystallographic analysis."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000853> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020131>)
