# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000868> (natural organic material)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000868> "natural organic material"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000868> "Natural organic materials are materials derived from natural biological sources, primarily composed of carbon-based compounds."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000868> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000000>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000869> (occurence of chemical reaction)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000869> "occurence of chemical reaction"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000869> "The occurrence of (a) chemical reaction is the process in which substances interact to form new chemical compounds or alter their molecular structure."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000869> obo:BFO_0000015)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000870> (occurence of electic field)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000870> "occurence of electic field"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000870> "The occurrence of (an) electric field is a process describing the presence or generation of an electric field in a material or system."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000870> obo:BFO_0000015)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000871> (occurence of magnetic field)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000871> "occurence of magnetic field"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000871> "The occurrence of (a) magenetic field is a process describing the presence or generation of a magnetic field in a material or system."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000871> obo:BFO_0000015)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000877> (optical property)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000877> "optical property"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000877> "An optical property is a material property representing the characteristics that describe how a material interacts with light, including reflection, refraction, and absorption."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000877> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000005>)
