# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000880> (passing of time)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000880> "passing of time"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000880> "Passing of time is a process that describes the progression of time, which can influence material aging and property changes."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000880> obo:BFO_0000015)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000882> (phase boundary (realization))

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000882> "phase boundary (realization)"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000882> "A phase boundary is a realizable entity that is realized by the transition between distinct phases."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000882> obo:BFO_0000017)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000888> (polymer)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000888> "polymer"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000888> "A polymer is an engineered material that consists of many repeated subunits (monomers) to form long chains. The atoms within a polymer chain are bonded together by covalent bonds. The intermolecular forces between polymer chains are typically represented by Van der Waals forces and hydrogen bonds."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000888> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000002>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000890> (connected material entity aggregate)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000890> "connected material entity aggregate"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000890> "A material entity aggregate that is a mereological sum of separate material entities, which adhere to one another through chemical bonds or physical junctions that go beyond gravity."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000890> "the atoms of a molecule, the molecules forming the membrane of a cell, the epidermis in a human body"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000890> obo:BFO_0000027)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000891> (disconnected material entity aggregate)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000891> "disconnected material entity aggregate"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000891> "A material entity aggregate that is a mereological sum of scattered (i.e. spatially separated) material entities, which do not adhere to one another through chemical bonds or physical junctions but, instead, relate to one another merely on grounds of metric proximity. The material entities are separated from one another through space or through other material entities that do not belong to the group."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000891> "a heap of stones, a colony of honeybees, a group of synapses, the trees of a forest, the canopy of a forest, the fish of a shoal, a group of commuters on the subway, the patients in a hospital"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000891> obo:BFO_0000027)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000896> (pressure)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000896> "The pressure is commonly measured in Pascals."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000896> "pressure"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000896> "The pressure is a thermodynamic quality describing the force exerted per unit area on a material."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000896> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020131>)
DisjointClasses(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000896> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000967>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000899> (Urformen)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000899> "Urformen"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000899> "primary shaping"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:altLabel <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000899> "Primary Forming"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000899> "A manufacturing process that creates a defined workpiece from shapeless material by producing cohesion, whereby the characteristic properties of the material become visible in the end product."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000899> "Ein Herstellungsprozess, der aus formlosem Stoff durch das Herstellen von Kohäsion ein definiertes Werkstück schafft, wobei die charakteristischen Eigenschaften des Materials im Endprodukt sichtbar werden."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000899> "Casting, Sintering"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000899> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000907> (Urformen Aus Dem Plastischen Zustand)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000907> "Urformen Aus Dem Plastischen Zustand"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000907> "primary shaping from the plastic state"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000907> "A Primary Shaping process that involves forming materials from a plastic state."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000907> "Ein Urformprozess, der das Formen von Materialien aus einem plastischen Zustand beinhaltet."@de)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:example <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000907> "Thermoforming of plastic sheets."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000907> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000899>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000933> (Simulationsprozess)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000933> "Simulationsprozess"@de)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000933> "simulation process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000933> "A Computing Process that models the behavior of a system over time using mathematical or computational techniques."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000933> "Ein Datenverarbeitungsprozess, der das Verhalten eines Systems im Laufe der Zeit mit mathematischen oder rechnerischen Techniken modelliert"@de)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000933> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000583>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000942> (specific surface area)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000942> "specific surface area"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000942> "The specific surface area is a morphologic quality describing the total surface area of a material per unit of mass or volume."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000942> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020131>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000949> (stiffness)

